    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This specimen is mechanically superlative, boasting a fully overhauled dual-VANOS system and proactively replaced rod bearings. The subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. Power is delivered through a precise six-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional traction and chassis feedback. The engine utilizes individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response, and the valvetrain is in perfect synchronization. With zero deferred maintenance and a factory-spec interior, this is a turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
