      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours-level condition. The S54 3.2L inline-six remains a masterpiece of atmospheric engineering, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This example features a documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, ensuring the structural and timing integrity of the chassis and powertrain. The suspension geometry remains factory-spec with zero bushing deflection, while the limited-slip differential provides optimal torque distribution. Every panel retains its factory tolerances, and the undercarriage is free of oxidation, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and rigorous preventative maintenance. A rare opportunity for the purist seeking a mechanically uncompromised driving machine.",
